  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK1024">
<l>cūḻāmaṟ ṟāṉē muṭiveytuṅ taṅkuṭiyait</l>
<l>tāḻā tuñaṟṟu pavarkku</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Those who are prompt in their efforts (to better their family) need no deliberation, such efforts will of themselves succeed.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
